---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="FidoHikes privacy policy — how we handle your data." disableOneTag={true}>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-800 text-earth mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="prose">
      <p><em>Last updated: March 2026</em></p>
      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        FidoHikes is a static website. We do not collect personal information directly.
        We use analytics services to understand how visitors use our site.
      </p>
      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        We use Google Analytics to collect anonymous usage data including pages visited, time on site,
        and general geographic location. This data helps us improve our content.
      </p>
      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        Third-party services (analytics, affiliate networks) may set cookies on your browser.
        You can control cookies through your browser settings.
      </p>
      <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p>
        When you click affiliate links, the destination merchant may collect information
        according to their own privacy policy.
      </p>
      <h2>oneTag and Affiliate Optimization</h2>
      <p>
        If FidoHikes enables oneTag or similar affiliate optimization tools, those services may
        measure link and content performance to improve affiliate reporting. You can limit this
        kind of tracking through your browser privacy controls, cookie settings, or content
        blocking tools.
      </p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this policy? Email <a href="mailto:hello@fidohikes.com">hello@fidohikes.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
